Depends on
- ruby >= 1.9.3
- redis
- gem open4
- gem resque
- gem active_support/inflector
- gem srt
- mkvmerge
- subliminal

Modify /etc/transmission-daemon/settings.json
  "script-torrent-done-enabled": true 
  "script-torrent-done-filename": "/path/to/torrent-done.rb"

Modify /path/to/torrent-done.yaml to suit your needs

To enqueue manually, execute /path/to/torrent-done.rb <directory>